import { createApp } from "vue";
import App from "./App.vue";
createApp(App).mount("#app");
import MisaDialog from "./components/base/Dialog.vue";
import MisaButton from "./components/base/Button.vue"
import MisaCombobox from "./components/base/Combobox.vue"
import MisaContextMenu from "./components/base/Contextmenu.vue"
import MisaSearch from "./components/base/Search.vue"
import MisaInput from "./components/base/Input.vue"
import MisaNotify from "./components/base/Notify.vue"
const app = createApp(App)
app.component("m-dialog",MisaDialog)
app.component("m-button",MisaButton)
app.component("m-combobox",MisaCombobox)
app.component("m-contextmenu",MisaContextMenu)
app.component("m-search",MisaSearch)
app.component("m-input",MisaInput)
app.component("m-notify",MisaNotify)
app.mount('#app')
